---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Cocoboko Studios">
    <Navigation />
    
    <main class="bg-slate-800 min-h-screen text-white py-16">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
            
            <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
                    Last updated: December 31, 2025
                </p>

                <nav class="mb-10" aria-label="On this page">
                    <div class="border border-slate-600 rounded-lg p-4 bg-slate-900/40">
                        <p class="text-gray-300 font-semibold mb-2">On this page</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300">
                            <li><a href="#website-analytics" class="underline hover:no-underline">Website analytics (Simple Analytics)</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#email-updates" class="underline hover:no-underline">Email updates (MailerLite)</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </nav>

                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 id="website-analytics" class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Website analytics</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">
                        Cocoboko Studios values your privacy. This website uses <strong>Simple Analytics</strong> to collect anonymous, privacy-first usage data. No personal information is collected, and no cookies or tracking fingerprints are used.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Information Collection</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                        Simple Analytics collects basic anonymous usage data to help improve the browsing experience. This includes:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300">
                        <li>Page views and number of visits</li>
                        <li>Time spent on site (session duration)</li>
                        <li>Traffic sources and referring sites</li>
                        <li>Device type, browser version, and operating system</li>
                        <li>Approximate geolocation (country and region only)</li>
                        <li>Interaction metrics such as clicks and scroll depth</li>
                        <li>Browser and screen settings</li>
                        <li>Whether the visitor has Do Not Track (DNT) enabled</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Data Usage</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                        This information is used to:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300">
                        <li>Understand visitor behavior</li>
                        <li>Gain a general understanding of what types of content resonate with visitors</li>
                        <li>Identify technical issues</li>
                        <li>Better serve the Cocoboko Studios community</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Privacy Choices</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">
                        This website respects the “Do Not Track” (DNT) setting in your browser. If DNT is enabled, Simple Analytics still counts your visit, but does not store any identifiable metrics beyond that. You can also use browser settings or extensions to further restrict tracking.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section id="email-updates" class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Email updates (MailerLite)</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                        If you choose to sign up for email updates, we use <strong>MailerLite</strong> to collect and manage your email address and to send occasional emails when there is something worth sharing (for example: a game announcement, demo, or release).
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">What we collect</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-4">
                        <li>Your email address</li>
                        <li>Subscription metadata (such as the date/time you signed up and confirmation status)</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">How we use it</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-4">
                        <li>To send occasional updates you have opted in to receive</li>
                        <li>To maintain the mailing list (for example: preventing duplicates and honoring unsubscribe requests)</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Your choices</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-4">
                        <li>You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in any email</li>
                        <li>If you want your email removed entirely, you can contact us and we will delete it from our list</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p class="text-gray-300">
                        MailerLite may process this information on our behalf to provide the email service. We do not sell your email address.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>
